Portugal to Invite Companies to Study Shale Gas, Diario Reports

-- B y   J o a o   L i m a
-- 
2011-03-14T08:25:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-14/portugal-to-invite-companies-to-study-shale-gas-diario-reports.html
The  Portuguese government  plans to
invite a group of #oil companies to study the potential for
shale gas projects in  Portugal , Diario Economico reported,
citing Jose Perdigoto, director of the government’s geology and
energy department.  Portugal has a “geological strutcture with potential” and
the information is insufficient, Perdigoto said, according to
the Portuguese newspaper.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
